data.description: *NEW PAINT THROUGHOUT*NEW CARPET* Beautiful single story home sitting on HUGE LOT with 3 car garage and LOW HOA! Walk inside to a spacious front family room with ceiling fan light that is open to the dining area and kitchen! Sliding door takes you to the LARGE blank canvas backyard with enough room to fit a pool. Bedrooms have new carpet! Den has closet and can be converted to 3rd bedroom. Charming master bedroom has mirrored door walk in closet and master bathroom with double sinks and walk in shower. VIEW TODAY!!
